CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 5, 1966, pg. 2B reads: "Golden Wedding - Mr. and Mrs. George Henderson of 310 Carver St., celebrated their 50th wedding anniversary Jan. 16 with a family dinner and Open House at their home in East Liberty. Members of Sixth Mt. Zion Baptist Church, the Hendersons are parents of four children, Mrs. Dorothy Johnson, Catherine and Olive Hender[son] of East Liberty, and Walter of New Castle, as well as 12 grandchildren. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. George Henderson holding square "50" plaque, during fiftieth wedding anniversary celebration in home at 310 Carver Street, East Liberty
